<p>Get up and go: The blonde bombshell, 39, was clearly in an inspiring mood as she headed off to work for the day (pictured on Monday)</p>

<p>Meanwhile, last week the star begged fans to listen to Boris Johnson after the Prime Minister's latest address to the nation.</p>

